reviewText: In order to get Stanley and Iris cheaper than the listed $65.00 and up. I bought it packaged with Full Moon in Blue Water for $9.99. Stanley and Iris is a very well put together movie about every day people dealing with their own personal struggles. Well worth the time and investment. A great movie for the family to enjoy. Full Moon in Blue Water was good, but not for family viewing. Amazon delivery service was excellent as usual.
The DVD did not contain closed captioning, scene selection, and language preference features.
Stanley and Iris is one of my favorite Jane Fonda movies.  Love DeNiro in anything.
